2020.1.9
------------------------
Added functions isAllLower and adaptCase.
The latter adapts the case of the first argument to that of th second one,
until the first and second arguments differ, when compared case insensitively.

2017.12.8
-------------------------
Renamed the global boolean variable UTF8 to globUTF8.
Made some explicit type casts between int and size_t and changed some int
declarations to unsigned int declarations.